rComments: Such a nice professor with great infectious enthusiasm. She's so cute and easy-going, you could even enjoy snacks and write haiku in class in groups during class. All her lectures are attractive! Send her emails, and it is always a great time talking with her!

Wants you to engage with the material, but will make it easy because she's so involved and super fun! There's consistent work (some form of a project every week) and quite a bit of reading, but this is a pretty standard workload with a predictable result based on how much you put in.
